text: The 2014 China Open will be the eleventh super series tournament of the 2014 BWF Super Series. The tournament will be contested in Fuzhou, China from November 11–16, 2014 with a total purse of $700,000.http://bwfworldsuperseries.com/tournaments/2471/thaihot-china-open/ A qualification will occur to fill four places in all five disciplines of the main draws.
